[04:18:26.808] [INFO ]     Of course. Here is a detailed comparison of the pricing tiers for NovaLens Professional and NovaLens Business.
    
    ### NovaLens Professional vs. Business: Pricing Comparison
    
    | Feature | NovaLens Professional | NovaLens Business |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | **Target User** | Individual professionals, freelancers, small teams | Medium to large businesses, departments |
    | **Pricing Model** | Per-user, monthly subscription | Per-user, monthly or annual subscription |
    | **Price (Monthly)** | **$49 per user / month** | **$99 per user / month** |
    | **Price (Annual)** | **$44.10 per user / month** (billed as $529.20 annually, saving 10%) | **$89.10 per user / month** (billed as $1,069.20 annually, saving 10%) |
    | **Core Features** | All NovaLens Standard features, plus: <br> • Advanced AI model access (GPT-4, Claude 3 Opus)<br> • 5,000 AI credits/month<br> • Customizable AI workflows<br> • Priority email support | All NovaLens Professional features, plus: <br> • Unlimited AI credits<br> • Advanced team management & admin controls<br> • Single Sign-On (SSO) <br> • API access for integration<br> • Dedicated account manager & phone support |
    
    ### Key Differentiators
    
    1.  **Price:** The NovaLens Business tier is priced at **$99/user/month**, which is double the cost of the Professional tier at **$49/user/month**. This reflects the significant addition of enterprise-grade features.
    2.  **AI Credits:** The most substantial difference is in AI usage. The Professional plan includes 5,000 credits per month, suitable for heavy individual use. The Business plan offers **unlimited credits**, essential for teams with high-volume, continuous usage.
    3.  **Administration & Security:** The Business tier includes critical features for larger organizations, such as **SSO** for secure login and advanced **team management** controls, which are not available in the Professional tier.
    4.  **Support:** Professional includes priority email support, while Business upgrades this to a **dedicated account manager and phone support** for faster resolution of critical issues.
    
    In summary, choose **NovaLens Professional** for powerful individual or small-team use. Upgrade to **NovaLens Business** if your organization requires unlimited AI usage, enhanced security controls (SSO), API access, and premium, dedicated support.
